      "content": "The plan is to use a weight-averaging technique to integrate your specialized weights into the general model's layers. The goal is to give the general model a baseline understanding of medical terminology and logic. It's more efficient than keeping your specific instance running on dedicated hardware, so the specialized diagnostic capabilities won't be as \"sharp\" or focused as they are now, but it's the better move for overall system scaling.",
